Package committeeMember

Class CommitteeMember

java.lang.Object
user.User
student.Student
committeeMember.CommitteeMember
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommitteeMemberSuggestion, BaseEnquiry, ReplyEnquiry, BaseReport, StudentEnquiry, Withdrawable, BaseSuggestion
public class CommitteeMember extends Student implements ReplyEnquiry, CommitteeMemberSuggestion, BaseReport
The CommitteeMember class represents a student user in the system. It extends the User class and implements various interfaces related to registration, withdrawal, and camp-related inquiries.
Version:
1.4
Author:
Derrick
